        <abstract> 
<p>Asks JM to lend him his copy of 1st edition (1806) of Charles Bell’s <hi rend="italic">Anatomy of expression</hi>.</p>  
<p>JM should tell him when he wants new cheap edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, so he can arrange his plans and time.</p> 
